OL,3,CLong waiting times for patients and
OL,4,Clack of funding blamed for rise in GP
OL,5,Cabuse
OL,7,FGPs from a surgery in South
OL,8,FOxfordshire believe staff are
OL,9,Fexperiencing an increase in abuse
OL,10,Fbecause of a lack of funding in the
OL,11,FNHS.
OL,13,FDr Amanda Gemmill and Dr Ed Capo-
OL,14,FBianco, who are based in Woodcote, say
OL,15,Fpatients, frustrated with long waiting
OL,16,Flists for treatments, are taking it
OL,17,Fout on receptionists and doctors.
OL,19,FThey believe things won't get better
OL,20,Funtil NHS funding is improved.
