OL,5,Cabuse
OL,7,FSpeaking to ITV Meridian, Dr Gemmill
OL,8,Fsaid the amount of abuse is increasing.
OL,10,F"In the last few years we've seen
OL,11,Fpatients become upset, frustrated,
OL,12,Fangry and their behaviours have
OL,13,Fsometimes escalated beyond frustrated
OL,14,Fshouting to physical threatening
OL,15,Fviolence," she said.
OL,17,F"Banging on the desk, slamming doors,
OL,18,Fbeing physically threatening to
OL,19,Freception team members who are at the
OL,20,Ffront door of our building.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
