OL,3,CLong waiting times for patients and
OL,4,Clack of funding blamed for rise in GP
OL,5,Cabuse
OL,7,F"It's not a job for the faint-hearted.
OL,8,FOur reception team are warm and
OL,9,Ffriendly and kind yet they get faced
OL,10,Fwith a barrage of abuse on a daily
OL,11,Fbasis.
OL,13,F"And unfortunately those episodes can
OL,14,Foutweigh all the lovely, kind,
OL,15,Ffriendly patients and all the positive
OL,16,Ffeedback that they also get. We've
OL,17,Fdefinitely seen a high turnover in
OL,18,Fstaff and it is difficult to recruit
OL,19,Fbecause no one wants to come to work
OL,20,Fand feel threatened or unsafe."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
