OL,5,Cabuse
OL,7,FDr Ed Capo-Bianco added: "We've had
OL,8,Fthat directly where patients have
OL,9,Fquestioned a doctor's integrity based
OL,10,Fon their colour of the skin and their
OL,11,Fbackground and things which is
OL,12,Fentirely inappropriate.
OL,14,F"Unfortunately we've also had an
OL,15,Fincident with a patient getting very
OL,16,Fangry and upset at the front desk so
OL,17,Fmuch so that the receptionist was
OL,18,Ffearful for her safety and we had to
OL,19,Fcall the police.
