OL,3,CLong waiting times for patients and
OL,4,Clack of funding blamed for rise in GP
OL,5,Cabuse
OL,7,F"We've seen instances of our reception
OL,8,Fstaff, our front of house care
OL,9,Fnavigators having some quite difficult
OL,10,Fconversations with patients who are
OL,11,Foften coming from a point of view of
OL,12,Fthey're anxious, or they're in pain,
OL,13,For they're worried about something and
OL,14,Fjust don't feel that the health
OL,15,Fservice is meeting their demands.
