OL,3,CLong waiting times for patients and
OL,4,Clack of funding blamed for rise in GP
OL,5,Cabuse
OL,7,F"Our funding has just not kept up with
OL,8,Fthe rising demand, taking a smaller
OL,9,Fand smaller slice of what the NHS
OL,10,Ffunding is for providing the majority
OL,11,Fof the contacts and appointments that
OL,12,Fpeople have."
OL,14,FIn a statement a government
OL,15,Fspokesperson said: "Violent or abusive
OL,16,Fbehaviour towards general practice
OL,17,Fstaff is totally unacceptable and GPs
OL,18,Fhave our full support in refusing to
OL,19,Ftreat or reporting to police abusive
OL,20,Fpatients.
